      "text": [
        "579 - وَقَالَ أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَنْ جَدَّدَ قَبْراً أَوْ مَثَّلَ مِثَالاً فَقَدْ خَرَجَ مِنَ اَلْإِسْلاَمِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.579 - The Commander of the Faithful Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"Whoever renovates a grave or creates a figure (idol/statue) has exited Islam.\""
        ]
      }
    }
